::KitKat/DarkMouse/Battera/Shadow Wing::

DarkMouse:: She studied the scanners and waited for Megatron to send her on 
other tasks.  She glanced over at Scorponok and smiled.  She then returned 
to her scanning.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

KitKat:: She looked at the big red bot for a few more moments.  She got 
bored and went outside.  She saw Quickstrike and stringtra talking.  She 
went outside, past the two in the grass and went running into the trees. She 
went out over the hillside and into a small glen. She looked around and 
sniffed the air. "Hmm, I smell another wolf. I smell two male wolves in the 
area."  She ran to the other side of the glen.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Shadow Wing:: She went over to Prowl, "What will you have me do to help?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Battera:: She was near the entrance of the Destron base.  She could look 
outside and see daylight. She walked outside and spread her wings.  She took 
off and headed skyward. She flew in and out of the clouds, just enjoying the 
day and cool wind under her wings.
